    <item>
      <title>Best Paper Award at IEEE ISM 2017</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/news/best-paper-ism-2017/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2017 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/news/best-paper-ism-2017/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Congratulations to Randy Tan! His paper on real-time human activity analysis won the &lt;strong&gt;Best Paper Award&lt;/strong&gt; at the &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.ieeesmc.org/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;IEEE International Symposium on Multimedia (ISM) 2017&lt;/a&gt;, Workshop on Quality of Experience in Visual Media Processing and Transmission.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The work demonstrates a real-time system for recognizing and analyzing human activities from video, with applications in surveillance, healthcare monitoring, and interactive media.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
